title: Azure Event Hub Consumer Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: Input/Output Data This section includes information about the data type that the agent expects and delivers. The agent retrieves a message from the event hub and places it in a bytearray . The agent produces bytearray types. MIM For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see MIM .
